quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mbega tukwemere wewe mugihe abagowe aribo bagukurikira"
  26,112,"Nawe avuga ati:- nomenya gute ibikorwa vyanyu mwahora mugira"
  26,113,Iharurwa ryabo ntarihari atari ku muremyi wanje gusa iyo mwobimenya
  26,114,Nanje sinzo kwirukana abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,115,"Jewe ntaco ndimwo, atari uko ndimubatuza bari k’umugaragaro"
  26,116,"Nabo bavuga bati:- nutareka ewe Nuhu (iii) iryo tuza ryawe ntankeka uzoba uri mubazoterwa amabuye"
  26,117,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntankeka abantu banje banyihakanye"
  26,118,"Rero nuducire urubanza ruri hagati yanje hamwe nabo, urwo rubanza rube rwiza, kandi undokore hamwe nabo ndikumwe nabo hamwe n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,119,Kubera ivyo twaciye tumurokora hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose bari mubwato bwari butwaye ibintu vyinshi
  26,120,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi mubasigaye
  26,121,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,122,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,123,Na bene Aadi nabo barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,124,"Mugihe\tmwene\twabo\tHudu\t(iii)\tyababwira\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimuzotinya Imana yanyu"
  26,125,Ntankeka jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,126,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, kandi mungamburukire"
  26,127,"Kandi\tntaco\tnshaka\tkuri\tibi\tvyose,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri\tku muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,128,"Mbega mwiyubakira amazu ahari agatumba, uku n’ugufyinata muriko muragira"
  26,129,Mukiyubakira n’inzitiro nk’uko mubona yuko muzoramba mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  26,130,No mugihe muteye abandi mubatera n’ubwishime
  26,131,Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,132,Nimutinye uwabahaye ibi vyose muzi
  26,133,Ko ariwe yabahaye ibikoko hamwe n’ibibondo vy’abahungu
  26,134,Hamwe n’imirima n’amasoko y’amazi n’inzuzi
  26,135,Mu vy’ukuri ndabafitiye ubwoba bw’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka
  26,136,"Nabo bamwishuye bati:- n’ibisanzwe kuri twebwe\tkuko udushikirije ubwo butumwa canke ntube mubabu dushikiriza"
  26,137,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ingeso z’abantu baho hambere
  26,138,Natwe ntituzohanwa
  26,139,"Rero baramuhakana natwe duca tubibiza mumazi, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mu bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,140,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,141,Bene Thamuda nabo nyene barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,142,"Mugihe mwene wabo yabwira intumwa y’Imana Swaleh (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,143,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,144,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,145,"Kandi nanje sindabasaba impembo kuri ivyo, mugabo impembo yanje iri ku muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,146,Mbega muzosigwa mumahoro muri ibi bintu biri ngaha iwanyu
  26,147,Mumirima hamwe no mumasoko y’amazi
  26,148,N’ibiterwa vy’imitende bifise ivyamwa vyiza
  26,149,Mukabaza n’imisozi nukuyigira mwo amazu yanyu y’ukwinezereza mwo gusa
  26,150,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,151,Kandi ntimu gamburukire amategeko yabo bahakanyi b’Imana
  26,152,Nabagira ubwononyi gusa kuri iy’Isi mugabo ntibayigire neza
  26,153,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,154,"Wewe\tntanakimwe\turimwo\tahubwo\turi\tumuntu\tnkatwe,\trero nutuzanire ibitangaro niwaba uvugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,155,"Nawe abishura ati:- iyi nyana y’Ingamiya nibe ifise izamu\tryukunywa amazi, namwe mube mufise izamu ryanyu ryukuvoma k’umusi wageneweko"
  26,156,"Kandi ntimuyikoreko ngo muyigirire inabi\thanyuma ntimuze mufatwe n’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka"
  26,157,Mugabo abo bantu barayikereye iyo Ngamiya nukuba mumaganya
  26,158,"Rero ibihano birabafata, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibavyemera"
  26,159,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,160,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,161,"Mugihe yababwira mwene wabo na Lutwi (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,162,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,163,"Rero ni mutinye Imana yanyu, nanje mu ngamburukire"
  26,164,"Kandi jewe sindabasaba impembo kuri ibi vyose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumana w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,165,Mbega mwebwe murangura amabanga yabubatse n’abagabo nkamwe mubiremwa vy’imana
  26,166,"Mukareka\tabo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tyabaremeye\tmubagore\tbanyu,\tmu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mubantu mwarenze uburimbi"
  26,167,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- nutareka kutubuza wewe Lutwi (iii) ntankeka wewe uzoba uri mubantu bazokwirukanwa ngaha muri iki gisagara turimwo"
  26,168,"Nawe abishura ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndimu bantu banka cane ivyo bikorwa vyanyu bigaritse vy’umwanda"
  26,169,Muremyi wanje nundokore n’aba bantu banje kuri ibi bintu bariko baragira
  26,170,Natwe duca turamurokora n’abantu biwe bose
  26,171,Dukuyemwo umutamakazi yari mubicara inyuma y’abandi bose
  26,172,Hanyuma duca turabahonya b’abandi
  26,173,"Duca tubamanurira imvura y’isegenya mbi cane, nayo yari iyaba gabishijwe"
  26,174,"Ntankeka ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,175,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,176,N’abantu bo mukibira nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,177,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Shuebu (iii) yababwira ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,178,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,179,Nimutinye Imana yanyu kandi mu ngamburukire
  26,180,"Kandi sindabasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"